Study Planner Dashboard 🚀
A modern, responsive dashboard built with React & Tailwind CSS to help you organize study tasks, track your progress, and boost productivity.

(Replace the link above with a screenshot of your project)

✨ Core Features
📝 Task Management: Full CRUD functionality with search and filters.

📊 Analytics: Track your productivity with insightful charts.

📅 Calendar View: Visualize your tasks and due dates.

🌗 Light & Dark Mode: A sleek, themeable interface.

🍅 Pomodoro Timer: A built-in timer to stay focused.

⚙️ Custom Settings: Personalize your experience and export/import your data.

🛠️ Built With
React

Tailwind CSS

React Router

Recharts

Lucide Icons

🚀 Quick Start
Clone the repository:

Bash

git clone https://github.com/your-username/study-planner.git
Install dependencies:

Bash

npm install
Run the app:

Bash

npm run dev
The app will be running on http://localhost:5173. Enjoy!
